// entity 7 — M10 reference enemy (far east). Map-placeable via `"classname"
// "reference_enemy"` because its descriptor (sdk/behaviors/reference/entities.ts,
// spread into the dev mod through `...referenceEntities`) carries health + mesh.
// It also carries the `ai` brain (detection/attack/leash, attackDamage,
// attackCooldownMs, moveSpeed, deathDespawnMs, and the idle/alert/attack/death
// -> mesh-state map). The CC0 KayKit Knight model animates the four FSM states.
// Placed far east behind the center pillar so reaching the player requires the
// A* + funnel detour; the shipped reference pistol's hitscan kills it
// (health max 60 + hitbox).
{
"classname" "reference_enemy"
"origin" "944 256 16"
"angles" "0 180 0"
"_tags" "enemy"
}
